Class AVLTreeNode<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>,P>

  • java.lang.Object
    • AVLTreeNode<T,P>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - extends Comparable : Item of node (String substring)
    P - : Pair that goes into the node's LinkedList (IndexPair pair)

    public class AVLTreeNode<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>,P>
extends java.lang.Object
    A generic node of AVL tree. Each node contains a substring and LinkedList consisting of the substring's indices.
